claim.claim-text:
A display device, comprising:
a display panel;
a bottom container member which receives the display panel;
an auxiliary member coupled with the bottom container member, and comprising a bottom, and a side extending from a first edge of the bottom;
a light source unit coupled with the side of the auxiliary member; and
a first heat radiating member between the side of the auxiliary member and the light source unit,
wherein the first heat radiating member comprises a first phase change material.
